head_commit.message:
metrics: add worker_park_unpark_count

This counts the number of times a worker was
parked and unparked. Thus it is odd if the worker
is parked and even if the worker is unparked.

head_commit.message:
metrics: add worker thread id

This allows querying the thread id of each worker thread.

Additional information, such as native thread id, can be
collected using runtime::Builder::on_thread_start() and
correlated using the thread id.
